# 🤖 Enci — AI Chatbot Widget
### by Encegen AI Labs Pvt Ltd

> **Enci** is a fully-featured AI-powered chatbot widget built with React + FastAPI.  
> It floats in the bottom-right corner of any website and handles lead capture, meeting scheduling, and AI-powered conversations — all powered by Groq (LLaMA 3).

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
encegen-project/
│
├── backend/                        ← Python FastAPI server
│   ├── main.py                     ← API routes: /api/chat, /api/leads, /api/bookings
│   ├── database.py                 ← SQLite database (leads + bookings)
│   ├── email_service.py            ← Email notifications via GoDaddy SMTP
│   ├── requirements.txt            ← Python dependencies
│   └── .env.example                ← Environment variable template
│
├── frontend/                       ← React chatbot widget
│   ├── public/
│   │   └── Encegen_logo.jpg        ← ⬅ Your company logo (place here)
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── components/
│   │   │   └── EncegenChatWidget.jsx   ← Main widget (all UI + logic)
│   │   ├── lib/
│   │   │   └── api.js              ← Backend API client
│   │   ├── App.jsx                 ← Mounts the widget
│   │   ├── main.jsx
│   │   └── index.css
│   ├── index.html
│   ├── package.json
│   └── vite.config.js
│
├── README.md                       ← This file
├── INTEGRATION.md                  ← Embedding guide
└── EMAIL_SETUP.md                  ← Email configuration guide
```

---

## ✨ Features

| Feature | Description |
|---|---|
| 🤖 **AI Chat** | Powered by Groq (LLaMA 3.1-8B) — fast, accurate responses |
| 📋 **Lead Capture** | Automatically detects and saves qualified leads |
| 📅 **Meeting Scheduler** | 3-step booking flow with calendar + time slots |
| 📧 **Email Notifications** | Instant email alerts for new leads and bookings |
| 💬 **Suggestion Chips** | Smart follow-up question buttons after each response |
| 🕐 **Chat History** | Saves and restores previous conversations |
| 😊 **Emoji Picker** | Built-in emoji support in the message input |
| 📱 **Fully Responsive** | Works on desktop and mobile browsers |
| 🎨 **Animations** | Float, blink, ripple, spring — professional UI |
| 🛡️ **Strict Lead Validation** | Only saves leads with name + phone/email |

